### Step 6: Verify and Run All Checks

**Commands to Run**:
```bash
# Check for suppressed warnings (should produce NO OUTPUT)
rg -n -U --pcre2 '(?x)\#\s*!?\[\s*(allow|expect)\s*\(' --glob '!target/**' --glob '!.git/**' --glob '*.rs' .

rg -n -U --pcre2 '(?x)\#\s*!?\[\s*cfg_attr\s*\([^()]*?\b(allow|expect)\s*\(' --glob '!target/**' --glob '!.git/**' --glob '*.rs' .

# Format and check
cargo fmt --all
cargo clippy --all-targets --all-features -- -D warnings

# Run all tests
cargo test --all-features
```

**Expected Outcome**:
- No suppressed warnings
- No clippy warnings
- All tests pass, including the integration test that was previously failing

